8月8日，[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]西南海岸形成了一股热带低气压，低气压向西漂移，于次日增强为热带风暴并开始加速朝西北方向行进。接近[[美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区|美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区]]后，气旋的[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]估计达到了每小时130公里，达到了如今[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的一级飓风标准。飓风逼近阿拉巴马州和佛罗里达州边界，并在陆地上空减弱后蜿蜒西进。<ref name="HURDAT" />8月12日，风暴漂移至[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]和[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]上空，给两州带去了倾盆大雨<ref name="MWR2">{{cite journal | volume = 39 | issue = 8 | work = Monthly Weather Review | publisher = American Meteorological Society | pages = 1149-1150 | date = 1911-08 | accessdate = 2010-04-29 | title = The Small Hurricane of August 11–12, 1911 at Pensacola, FLA | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/039/mwr-039-08-1149.pdf | format = PDF | author = Reed, W. F | bibcode = 1911MWRv...39.1149R | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1911)39<1149:TSHOAA>2.0.CO;2 | issn = 1520-0493 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131217215147/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/039/mwr-039-08-1149.pdf | archivedate = 2013-12-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

1911年8月11日晚，佛罗里达州的彭萨科拉出现了时速130公里的狂风，低压则低至1007毫巴（百帕，29.73英寸汞柱）。随着飓风[[风眼|风眼]]的经过，当地进入了一段短暂的平静期，然后情况再度恶化。风暴产生的降雨量总计达到114[[毫米|毫米]]，狂风导致[[电话|电话]]和[[电报|电报]]线路中断<ref name="MWR2" />，令当地与外界失去联系达24小时。该市当晚也出现了大范围[[停电|停电]]<ref name="NYT">{{cite news | author =  | title = Pensacola Storm Loss Big.; No Lives Lost in City, but Much Damage to Property. | date = 1911-08-13 | work = The New York Times | accessdate = 2014-03-01 | archivedate = 2012-11-11 | publisher = The New York Times Company | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121111162325/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9804EEDF123AE633A25750C1A96E9C946096D6CF | deadurl = no | url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9804EEDF123AE633A25750C1A96E9C946096D6CF }}</ref>。航运业损失惨重，许多驳船被狂风吹至触礁搁浅<ref name="NYT" /><ref>{{cite news | author =  | title = Terrific Gale Hits Gulf Coast;Vessels and Shipping Suffer Widespread Loss at Pensacola, Fla.;One Big Ocean Liner Ashore in Shallow Water; Many Barges Ashore;Wind Reaches Velocity of at Least Eighty Miles an Hour at Night | date = 1911-08-12 | work = The Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2014-03-01 | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/159557514.html?FMT=CITE&FMTS=CITE:AI&type=historic&date=Aug%2012,%201911&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=ELEMENTS%20RUN%20RIOT | archive-date = 2016-03-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307074207/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/159557514.html?FMT=CITE&FMTS=CITE:AI&type=historic&date=Aug%2012,%201911&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=ELEMENTS%20RUN%20RIOT | dead-url = no }}</ref>。这场飓风把保存在沿海“数量庞大”的木材吹得四下分散<ref name="NYT" />，飓风造成的死亡人员至今仍无定论<ref name="NYT" />。虽然这场风暴造成了严重的破坏，但根据1911年8月发行的《[[每月天气回顾|每月天气回顾]]》（{{lang|en|''Monthly Weather Review''}}）描述，其影响还是小于预期，彭萨科拉遭受的损失共计约为12000[[美元|美元]]（1911年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|12000|1911}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）。阿拉巴马州的[[莫比尔_(阿拉巴马州)|莫比尔]]记录到每小时56公里的大风，但没有造成损失的报告<ref name="MWR2" />。
